---
const faqs = [
  {
    q: "Is Breaks really free?",
    a: "Yes. Free, MIT-licensed, no in-app purchases, no account, no analytics, nothing leaves your machine. State lives in macOS UserDefaults under the bundle ID.",
  },
  {
    q: "Why do I get an 'unidentified developer' warning?",
    a: "Breaks isn't notarized by Apple yet. Notarization requires a $99/year Apple Developer membership. Until then, right-click the app and choose Open on first launch, or run xattr -dr com.apple.quarantine /Applications/Breaks.app once.",
  },
  {
    q: "Does it work on Intel Macs?",
    a: "Yes. Releases ship as a universal binary (arm64 + x86_64), so the same zip runs on Apple Silicon and Intel Macs.",
  },
  {
    q: "What happens if I close my laptop mid-session?",
    a: "Breaks watches sleep and wake notifications, then reconciles the timer against an end-date so it doesn't drift. Open the lid an hour later and the session is right where it should be (or finished, if the time elapsed).",
  },
  {
    q: "What about idle time?",
    a: "If you walk away for longer than your idle threshold, Breaks notices and asks whether the just-elapsed time should still count toward the session. You decide.",
  },
  {
    q: "How do streaks survive missed days?",
    a: "Each ISO week comes with a small pause-day budget. The first N missed days that week are absorbed before the streak starts decaying. Configurable in settings.",
  },
  {
    q: "Will there be auto-updates?",
    a: "Sparkle is on the roadmap. For now, watch the GitHub repo or check Releases. New versions are tag-driven and ship on the same day they're built.",
  },
  {
    q: "Where can I file bugs or request features?",
    a: "GitHub Issues is the right place. The roadmap is a public Project on the same repo.",
  },
];
---

<section id="faq" class="faq">
  <div class="wrap">
    <header class="head">
      <span class="eyebrow">Questions</span>
      <h2 class="serif">Things people ask first.</h2>
    </header>

    <div class="list" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/FAQPage">
      {
        faqs.map((f) => (
          <details
            class="item"
            itemscope
            itemprop="mainEntity"
            itemtype="https://schema.org/Question"
          >
            <summary>
              <span itemprop="name" class="q">{f.q}</span>
              <span class="caret" aria-hidden="true">+</span>
            </summary>
            <div
              class="a"
              itemscope
              itemprop="acceptedAnswer"
              itemtype="https://schema.org/Answer"
            >
              <p itemprop="text">{f.a}</p>
            </div>
          </details>
        ))
      }
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .faq {
    padding-block: clamp(4rem, 9vw, 7rem);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--hair);
  }
  .head {
    display: grid;
    gap: 1rem;
    max-width: 30ch;
    margin-bottom: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3rem);
  }
  .head h2 {
    font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 3.6vw, 2.6rem);
    line-height: 1.1;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    font-weight: 400;
    font-variation-settings: "opsz" 100, "SOFT" 70;
  }

  .list {
    max-width: 80ch;
  }
  .item {
    border-top: 1px solid var(--hair);
    padding: 1.1rem 0;
  }
  .item:last-of-type {
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--hair);
  }
  summary {
    list-style: none;
    cursor: pointer;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    padding-block: 0.2rem;
  }
  summary::-webkit-details-marker {
    display: none;
  }
  .q {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: clamp(1.05rem, 1.6vw, 1.25rem);
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.3;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    color: var(--ink);
    font-variation-settings: "opsz" 36, "SOFT" 70;
  }
  .caret {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--ink-mute);
    width: 1.4rem;
    text-align: center;
    transition: transform 0.2s ease, color 0.2s ease;
  }
  .item[open] .caret {
    transform: rotate(45deg);
    color: var(--amber);
  }
  .a {
    overflow: hidden;
    padding-top: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--ink-dim);
    line-height: 1.65;
    font-size: 1rem;
    max-width: 64ch;
  }
  .item[open] .a {
    animation: drop 280ms ease both;
  }
  @keyframes drop {
    from {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(-4px);
    }
    to {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
  }
</style>
